extendedInfo.description: Nicolet Mobile Deposit allows you to quickly, easily and conveniently use your smart phone to securely deposit checks into your Nicolet checking account. To enroll, go to the Android Market and download the Nicolet app.  Click sign up and enter the required information.  You will receive an email telling you when you can start depositing checks to your account remotely.Deposits made before 5:30 p.m. CST will be processed the same business day.  Deposits made after 5:30 p.m. CST will be processed the next business day.  All other terms and conditions related to your account apply.If you have questions or problems, please contact customer support at 855-451-4791.
